rComments: Prof is very unappreciative, rude and doesn't encourage any motivation to actually learn from her. If you like and want to learn painting I suggest you take this class w a diff professor, because she might really make you hate this class.
Very helpful prof. Strict, but pushes you to  your potential. Provided a great reference for me and encouraged my ideas.
